data.eml:eml: Chronicle of Nature - Phenology of Mushrooms of Kondinskie Lakes National Park named after L. F. Stashkevich

Mushrooms Phenology dataset compiled in the context of Chronicle of Nature program in Kondinskie Lakes National Park named after L. F. Stashkevich (Russian Federation) consisting of 224 records collected during 16 years between 2000 and 2015.
